Kullec yettmettat kellec ikeffu 
Seg lmut I d-tekkek tudert
tudert tetteffeγ γer lmut
ṣṣura-nneɣ d ṣṣura n lmut 
acu kan lmut d tasarutt n tudert akken inna Jean-Lmuhuv Amruc
Yiwen uderɣal la ilehhu, irrat-id lḥid, inna-yas : « syagi i tuɣal ddunit! » 
Wwet kan a Xali Muḥ! 
I d as-inna Muḥya deg wawal-is
Yal yiwen seg-neɣ teḥbes tmussni-ines 
anda iḥbes netta anadi
Immer am wayen kra d-itteffɣen d idlisen d wayen ttarun wiyaḍ
ur nettraju ara ad mucaɛen 
ad nettili kan seg yimeɣra imenza
ssakin wa immal i wa
Tira n umeskar tessenṭi am tefsut
tissenṭit a tebda-d gar taggara n hertadem d tegrest
mazal ur tensi tmes ur insi lbarud n ccna
Tewwi-d isalen n dihin, tessefra γef dagi
tessarem i tafrara n dihin
Akli iban kan iẓra ayen iruḥ iẓra amek ma iqqim
amar deg yisefra yagi 
ad d-naf ahat amek iẓra
Tura taffa-yagi n yeḍrisen 
isefra nniden ur sen ittumecc ara uzref
Gan amkan itayri n tmurt
Tayri n umezruy d tidett 
I ten id-ifernen am ujilban seg uḥbac
ṭṭredqen am umud n uḥlalas
Targit teqqar i ta aẓ akkin
tirga yagi swant-d seg urawen tilawt
seg tidett qerriḥen n watas n temsal 
tayri warisem
lɣerba d uɣbel n tmurt n Iqbayliyen 
Timseḍra s-d-iddurin amnaṛ
Tifsuyin tizegzawin, tizeggaγin d tberkanin
Amedyaz macci yiwen n uɛbaṛ i yessuffeɣ
kra seg-sen neqqen
Wiyaḍ ttaken-d tudert
